				<description>&lt;section id=&#34;showcase&#34; class=&#34;rad-showcase cyber-hero&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;cyber-hero__gridbg&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;canvas class=&#34;cyber-hero__canvas&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/canvas&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;cyber-hero__inner&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;cyber-hero__text&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;cyber-hero__label&#34;&gt;&amp;lt; Forensic Engineer &amp;amp; Cyber Security /&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h1 class=&#34;cyber-hero__name&#34;&gt;EREN ÖNDER&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;cyber-hero__role&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;cyber-hero__role-prefix&#34;&gt;I&amp;#39;m a&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;span class=&#34;cyber-hero__role-word&#34; data-typewriter data-words=&#34;Associate Cyber Security Analyst|SOC Analyst|Security Researcher|Forensic Engineer|CTF Player&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;cyber-hero__bio&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&#39;m Eren ÖNDER, a 4th-year Digital Forensic Engineering student at Fırat University, working actively across offensive and defensive cybersecurity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a CTF competitor, organizer, instructor and researcher, I pursue a career that is both technically deep and gives back to the community — from national projects and published research to seminars and large student communities.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
